# Title: Kubernetes Events Deleted
# Author: Leo Tsaousis (@laripping)
# Date: 2024-03-26
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when events are deleted in Kubernetes.
# An adversary may delete Kubernetes events in an attempt to evade detection.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1070
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/application/kubernetes/audit/kubernetes_audit_events_deleted.yml

objectRef.resource="events" verb="delete"